{"tid":1795602,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[集思廣益] <光復香港，時代革命> 車牌設計募集","createTime":"2019-12-24T04:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T05:34:05.000Z","uid":126841,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"758c10a42240aa540e1862cff5791425831dfb1e","tid":1795602,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我係一個係喺美國嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n之前自己自製咗個光復香港旗，約咗班在美港人一齊行山影相支持香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2u2OmT0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2u2OmT0.jpg&h=8b157223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太樣衰要遮下個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">btw</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我有位好朋友忽發奇想<br />\n<br />\n想試下係美國呢到設計一個美國關於香港既車牌去登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解係車牌呢？？？<br />\n<br />\n喺美國，大部分家庭點都要有車<br />\n<br />\n每個人買車都要有個車牌鑲係bumper到<br />\n<br />\n有興趣地，原來美國每個州嘅車牌都有唔同既design<br />\n<br />\n比如<br />\n<br />\n加州<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TaL8CU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TaL8CU.png&h=bd32816d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我住Virginia 嘅車牌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HNaz1W5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHNaz1W5.png&h=eefd7aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我哋就係到諗喇，我地可唔可以一齊設計返個光復香港嘅車牌呢？？<br />\n<br />\n一個車牌size係 闊6吋x高3吋（以我住Virginia做參考）<br />\n<br />\n左上角加右上角要貼車嘅登記資訊 上面中間要寫返州名<br />\n<br />\n下面加個Free Hong Kong 有冇得諗？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有興趣幫手設計下？？<br />\n<br />\n如果有靚design嘅話，我地可唔可以搵個最靚嘅design然後我去登記個關於香港嘅車牌設計？<br />\n<br />\n我知道我哋呢個諗法好天馬行空，但係Friends of Tibet 個車牌啟發咗我朋友，我哋都想整個Hong Kong 車牌鑲喺我哋架車前面。諗諗成件事其實好型，可以喺美國做文宣，又可以俾多啲司機欣賞香港人嘅創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b5eab178e5ef97e11b1577133c9b4a4ccd66b3","tid":1795602,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"Sorry 第一個post 未寫好就post咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bdff32ff13acdce99dab25f0322a5a817ff058","tid":1795602,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"有冇設計師想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />??"},{"pid":"5ec2082097b8006a7ca0583ab975c384bdeca113","tid":1795602,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd16369320c14034c9fb2d107193661d188b5cf","tid":1795602,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:49:46.000Z","msg":"有冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"577d7b2a6966d6aa8d40ff18264c35306c7e6e6c","tid":1795602,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:57:33.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c6e68f824ad842acf9a176653d9865394e6ebd","tid":1795602,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"7c8a04a6b7f100fa557d48684ffa26300e63b8ef","tid":1795602,"uid":306614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:20:08.000Z","msg":"sounds like good promotion push"},{"pid":"31b908312728b2f744464b0347e155320a50b587","tid":1795602,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c8a04a6b7f100fa557d48684ffa26300e63b8ef","tid":1795602,"uid":306614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:20:08.000Z","msg":"sounds like good promotion push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:11:57.000Z","m